casebody.head_matter:
Stacy PARTIN, petitioner,
v.
Ron H. TILFORD.
No. 17-7377.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 19, 2018.
Motion of respondent to substitute Rose M. Tilford, Executrix of the Estate of Ron H. Tilford as respondent in place of Ron H. Tilford, Deceased granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.
